{"id": "1458075711444221962", "channel_id": "1458075711444221962", "type": 0, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "【防剧透】\n\n~~我终于开始推主线了，如果我问了个蠢问题，请见谅<:takenotes:1357186646294138890> ~~\n\n从第七章尾声那里我们应该知道威廉学长死透了，他的遗体没有银芯析出，但在第八章共鸣那一边，威廉又出现了\n\n起初我还以为这只是某种回忆一样的介绍，但是在共鸣这里也同时出现了第七章后才加入弥萨格的艾尔瓦\n\n因此，基本可以很肯定这不是一种回忆录吧？\n\n问题就是在第七章威廉离去了，艾尔瓦加入了，第八章共鸣这边同时有威廉和艾尔瓦的存在是不是怪怪的？这两个介绍的时间线难道不同吗<:question1:1356085150869622965>", "timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:32:19.345000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-06T12:47:29.708000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1458075711771508841", "filename": "Screenshot_20260106_192840.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 65840, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458075711444221962/1458075711771508841/Screenshot_20260106_192840.jpg?ex=69ff2953&is=69fdd7d3&hm=677ae27d2352f682842abf9f073ba4470dd5d08edf2bc01732d7bc26847ae991&"}, {"id": "1458075712375226439", "filename": "Screenshot_20260106_192844.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 66711, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458075711444221962/1458075712375226439/Screenshot_20260106_192844.jpg?ex=69ff2953&is=69fdd7d3&hm=6ece6c4cd22a0ea7c9a1934636a903f0de79f4d224daec326a6b594099aa73ee&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458075711444221962", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我有个剧情上的疑惑(第八章)", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
